--------------------------------------------------------------------------
GUILD RECRUITING
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Wizards or higher will NOT recruit players for any guild.  If a player asks
a wizards o question on a guild, they should be told that they need to talk
to other players to determine that information.  It doesn't matter if you
coded the guild in question, you will not recruit players for it.  Doing
so is a breach of the wizard/player non-involvement rule and will be frowned
upon.  Repeated infractions will be punished.
